<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA55">
<l>paṇṭamara rañcap paṭukaṭali ṉañcuṇṭu</l>
<l>kaṇṭaṅ kaṟuttatuvu maṉṟiyē - yuṇṭu</l>
<l>paṇiyuṟuvār ceñcaṭaimēṟ pāṉmatiyi ṉuḷḷē</l>
<l>maṇimaṟuvāyt tōṉṟum vaṭu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Besides [your] throat being blackened by eating the poison from the</l>
<l>moving ocean, so that the immortals once were afraid, there is</l>
<l>the stain that appears as a flaw in the gem, in the milk moon</l>
<l>on the flowing red matted hair with snakes.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
